Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:14.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何ページもついやして　綴られた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:21.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうしてか一行の　空白をうめられない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:29.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}押し花の栞はさんで　君と転がす使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:37.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れかけの煉瓦を　積み上げた場所にゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:42.79,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}海を見渡す坂をかけのぼって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.34,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:55.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君をさがしている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:01:02.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうやって“今”は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:09.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ二人はすぐそこにいるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:15.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「どうかまた会えますように」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:25.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なんて　どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:14.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}使用好几页　填补了我们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:21.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却弥补不了那唯一的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:29.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夹上干花书签　和你乘上骑一次就扔的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:37.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往用几乎遗忘的砖头堆积起来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:42.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}爬上望得见海的小坡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}头上是湛蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:55.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}右手是碳酸饮料　左手一直在寻求着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:01:02.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在呢　你也不会再追问我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:09.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两个人明明还在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:15.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「而我却祈愿能再次相遇」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:25.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可能是我的错觉吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}出会いは　ふっとした　瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:39.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}声をかけてくれたね「一緒に帰ろう」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:46.50,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}あぁ　花火が夜空　きれいに咲いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:55.32,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}あぁ　風が時間とともに　流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:22:02.73,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}嬉しくって　楽しくって　冒険も　いろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:09.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}二人の　秘密の　基地の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:13.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:16.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}大きな希望を忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:24.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}10年後の8月　また出会えるのを　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君が最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}心から「ありがとう」叫んでたこと　知ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}涙をこらえて　笑顔でさようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:38.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}せつないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:47.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be5}最高の思い出を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}邂逅是瞬间的巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在回家的路口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:39.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}你对我说「一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:46.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}啊　烟花在夜空里绚丽地绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}有些伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:55.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}啊　风随着时间一起流动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:22:02.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}开心的　愉快的冒险也经历过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:09.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在两个人的秘密基地里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:13.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}不会忘记和你度过的夏天　将来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:16.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}和巨大的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:24.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}相信着十年后的八月还能与你再会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我知道你自始至终
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}都在心里喊「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}强忍泪水　笑着说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:38.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}有些伤感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:47.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be5}怀着最美好的回忆…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就成了还魂似的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了  芽间为了实现愿望而还魂回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得这只是我看到的幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想？也就是Fantasy？  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在也在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间是我啊  在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  芽间  露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然趁势就把芽间的事说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这些他能这么乖乖的接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  我看不见她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这只是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太果然太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密基地你在用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在日本的时候用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  那些红色的标记就是去过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看世界上各种各样的地方呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用打工挣的钱去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有时间去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子去了东南亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  越南的姑娘真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太真强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那么小的个子  现在长这么壮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  变了不少哦  Jungle Cruise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑题了跑题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的愿望是吧  有过什么约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是曾说过想要仁太的「是的哦」的签名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是的哦」哪至于变鬼还要来取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的栗丸怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去后给你吃酸奶哦酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子你真的去了宿海家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去照顾家里蹲真是倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶尔不是有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么没精神 早上很辛苦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也偶尔会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦  但我不想被视为那阴沉的家伙的同类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在绝对在拿鸣子想色色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王大附属的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤…鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就不要管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和绿高的女生说话的情形要是被谁看见的话太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思  等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心给你送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}你什么时候这么高傲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣  鹤子  不能吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}以前明明那么低调
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就容易被别人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和刚才你身边那些轻浮的女人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻浮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明一直在模仿本间芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死人的名字别随便挂在嘴边！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出自自己之口让自己痛苦  真没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想变得和芽间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  仁太是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:06:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢芽间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我没有那样挑动他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁会喜欢这丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等仁太  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而后…变成了那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙在叫了就～回～家了  青蛙在叫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…应该回哪里去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要找什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  布袋妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人要买你有意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布袋妖怪哪一作  蛋白石？  绿宝石？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？布袋妖怪金  那是哪一年出的老古董了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之有卖的话就赶紧拿出来  赶紧卖给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  稀有布袋怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  芽间超想要的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直没能入手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像说过Bilbilder什么的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4571日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前出的游戏定价卖是不是太黑了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先申明了  这可是良心价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个已经绝版了  定价卖算便宜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事！谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来仁太君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天刚好从现场弄回来了很不错的盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吃烤肉大餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  没食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这算什么真不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么玩来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始三只里面选一只…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力具现化的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不该存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前那样叫噗噗就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热情点嘛  阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这叫法是第一次听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  对了雪集知道吗  仁太身边芽间还魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…宿海怎么说芽间的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他呢  好久不见了还是一如既往那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海怎么说芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听？还是幻想来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太懂  芽间好像说什么请实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间你回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…洗什么澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸也在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  总觉得洗澡除了凉飕飕外别无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间讨厌这样  仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀  对成长后的自己稍微注意一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然某部分还没怎么成长的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这少年好像哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好！好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  难道是噗噗？  好高！成长期真可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友交换？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  用连接线交换布袋妖怪后就可以获得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大叔  肉好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是昨晚的剩菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大叔我去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也说了「要大家一起才能实现」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害噗噗  怎么想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也看见幻听了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听不是看的是听的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样啊  那再买一个布袋妖怪的游戏卡就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  有布袋妖怪的人其他还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好可爱呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候最讨厌自己的卷发和眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔顺长发的芽间…被仁太喜爱的芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣  贴纸贴成成对的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给安鸣一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢芽间…却也很讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子  有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  连我也要玩布袋妖怪？开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系偶尔一玩  回归童心  是吧仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你俩来家里还真是怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚鸣子做的果冻吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣的果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再叫这名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之稀有布袋妖怪可是芽间的愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋别说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没…芽间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…在梦中出现了还是该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布袋妖怪在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  那是Love&Perry的卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是牛王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  牛王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直不过来这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为芽间在的话妈妈和安鸣都会变得伤心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bo☆BoBo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这么个小游戏上还贴名字…你真是规矩的人呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔了好久重新看Bo☆BoBo真是有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌不能相信  为什么没有波伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为稀有布袋妖怪不是要把波伊扎和钢格尔交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领域内没有波伊扎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让波伊特进化  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣果然没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大家很好  还有很多游戏漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种气氛总觉得好久不见了  真开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了  波伊扎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了  仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了  安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么  就当打发时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你的报酬有么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来上学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来把连接线接上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了这样就可以和朋友交换了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布袋妖怪到手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  这下芽间也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望好像不是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好事有许多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太安鸣还有噗噗又成了好朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不当自己事啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心摔倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没～关～系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间最近全是快乐的事～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的说哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间最近全是快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许久没这么快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神创伤虽然还没有消失的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然有明天的话  道歉就算慢慢来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始这样想了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔呵～烧烤真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜  肉  蔬菜  蔬菜  肉  得这样吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小香肠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该算肉…吧  加工肉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  听上去好强  加工～肉！
